{"tid":1736812,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[全民共識 認同就推] 唔玩陣地戰","createTime":"2019-11-18T20:27:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T11:29:36.000Z","uid":208046,"like":98,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"47cbb00bc2bcfb0e7af14828cf0e9576946f936e","tid":1736812,"uid":208046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T20:27:35.000Z","msg":"認同就推 推到全世界都睇到<br />\n<br />\n睇黎之後班狗會瘋狂放震撼彈黎瓦解陣地戰<br />\n長期對峙局面冇好結果 因為實在太唔對等<br />\n<br />\n轉地下形式行動快閃 令到對家防不勝防先係關鍵<br />\n裝修商場 / 紅店漸見成效<br />\n甚至快閃狗車都發生過<br />\n唔好再糾纏係死守同入夜對峙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後我真係好尊敬每一個肯為香港付出嘅手足<br />\n你地係唔會白費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba019cfe199cdeb0f7e4898f138dd53c1931d408","tid":1736812,"uid":14449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T20:29:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffce1cd7a00175c365b4223213bfecb7f820de68","tid":1736812,"uid":208046,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T20:29:38.000Z","msg":"另外大家唔該帶埋個腦上黎<br />\n唔好咁易睇完個topic就比人帶風向<br />\n班狗嘅其中一個策略就係不停講邊到邊到要人<br />\nPoly嘅Case就係咁樣發生"},{"pid":"c417858e575752b779863efa835e158ab0aef7e7","tid":1736812,"uid":201725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T20:29:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"86d16d7b814816f3f127d1e1563ce16c12c5a3cb","tid":1736812,"uid":208046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T20:29:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"648f387798718b4bc00666dc914e2fd5a75dacf7","tid":1736812,"uid":208046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T20:30:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b37cf9b2ed2d4d5b2e5201b1de23fa54d43649a0","tid":1736812,"uid":208046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T20: